Dancer
======

This repository is a fork of `jeremylongshore/claude-code-plugins`, renamed for
distinct namespace on 2026-04-20.

- Original work Copyright (c) 2025 Jeremy Longshore, licensed under MIT (see LICENSE).
- Modifications, additions, and Jack-authored plugins Copyright (c) 2026 Jack Reis,
  also licensed under MIT.

Per the MIT license, Jeremy's copyright notice and the MIT license text are
retained intact in the LICENSE file at the repository root. This NOTICE file is
additive — it does not modify or override the LICENSE.

Jack-authored plugins carry their own LICENSE files inside their plugin
directory (e.g. `plugins/ai-agency/autonomous-ai-agents/LICENSE`). Plugins
inherited from the upstream retain their original `author` field in
`plugin.json` — this fork does not claim authorship of upstream plugins.

The `name` field inside `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json` is `"dancer"` so that
Claude Code and other agents resolve this as a distinct marketplace from
Jeremy's upstream — without removing attribution to Jeremy's work.

For the original upstream: https://github.com/jeremylongshore/claude-code-plugins
